Examples and Demos
------------------

 - Added Spectrum analyzer demo application.
 - Added exit softkey to Wiggly example.
 - Added close button to Anomaly demo.
 - [BOBUIBUG-10635]: Fixed Anomaly demo controlstrip icon placement for very
