 - QXmlStreamReader
    * [BOBUIBUG-9196] Fixed crash when parsing.

BobUIGui
-----

 - QComboBox
    * [BOBUIBUG-10403] Fixed QComboBox ignoring the item data background role 
      for some styles.

 - QCommonStyle
    * [BOBUIBUG-7137] Fixed a bug that led to missing text pixels in BOBUIabBar when
      using small font sizes.

 - QCUPSSupport
    * [BOBUIBUG-10512] Fixed a potential crash with misconfigured CUPS printers.
    * [BOBUIBUG-6419] Make QCUPSSupport::printerHasPPD() release temporary file
      handles.

 - qDrawPixmaps()
    * [BOBUIBUG-8455] Fixed qDrawPixmaps() to draw on integer coordinates under
      Mac OS X.

 - QFontEngine
    * [BOBUIBUG-3976] Fixed a leak for QFont objects used in threads.

 - QGifHandler
    * [BOBUIBUG-7037] Fixed QGifHandler::loopCount().
    * [BOBUIBUG-6696] Cache the sizes of images in an animated GIF.

 - QGraphicsEffect
    * [BOBUIBUG-5358] Fixed warnings and crash when painting graphics effects
      outside scene.

 - QGraphicsItem
    * [BOBUIBUG-9391] Avoid a useless repaint when setting the cache mode to
      DeviceCoordinateMode while already using that mode.
    * [BOBUIBUG-8475] Fixed crash and loss of focus when deleting a child of a
      focus scope.

 - QGraphicsProxyWidget
    * [BOBUIBUG-5349] Fixed tooltips not being shown for QGraphicsProxyWidget.
    * [BOBUIBUG-2883] Fixed tooltips appearing at wrong location.
    * [BOBUIBUG-7296] Fixed painting artifacts on a scaled proxy when the view
      is scrolled.

 - QGraphicsScene
    * [BOBUIBUG-7863] Fixed incorrect blending when using
      QGraphicsItem::DeviceCoordinateCache and when the item is semi-
      transparent. If the item is transformed, the cache is now always fully
      repainted to avoid artifacts.

 - QGraphicsView
    * Item tooltips are not clipped by the view anymore.

 - QImageReader
    * [BOBUIBUG-7980] Fixed QImageReader::setAutoDetectImageFormat() to work with
      plugins.

 - QPainter
    * [BOBUIBUG-8140] Speed up custom bitmap brushes under X11 without Xrender
      support.
    * [BOBUIBUG-8032] Fixed drawing pixmaps onto bitmaps on X11 without Xrender
      support.
    * [BOBUIBUG-10421] Fixed WebKit-specific justification bug for text containing
      more than one script.

 - QPDFBaseEngine
    * [BOBUIBUG-8451] Fixed line and point drawing in the PS and PDF generators.

 - QPixmap
    * [BOBUIBUG-8606] Fixed QPixmap::load() to not modify referenced copies.

 - QPSPrintEngine
    * [BOBUIBUG-10121] Fixed incorrect version setting for EPS files.
    * [BOBUIBUG-10140] Fixed generation of the %%BoundingBox operator to output
      integer values instead of floating point values.

 - QRasterPaintEngine
    * [BOBUIBUG-9036] Fixed ClearType text rendering on translucent surfaces under
      Windows.

 - QRegion
    * [BOBUIBUG-7699] Prevented crash on large x-coordinates.

 - BOBUIextDocument
    * [BOBUIBUG-10301] Fixed a leak in BOBUIextDocument::print().

 - BOBUIextEdit
    * [BOBUIBUG-9599] Fixed crash when copying the current text cursor as a result
      of deleting a character.

 - BOBUIextEngine
    * [BOBUIBUG-9374] Fixed possible crash in BOBUIextEngine::boundingBox() when using
      multiscripted text.

 - BOBUIextLayout
    * [BOBUIBUG-9074] Fixed performance regression that was introduced in BobUI 4.6.0.

 - BOBUIransform
    * [BOBUIBUG-8557] Fixed bug in BOBUIransform::type() potentially occuring
      after using operator/ or operator* or their overloads.

 - BOBUIriangulatingStroker
    * [BOBUIBUG-9548] Fixed possible data corruption when certain paths were
      triangulated.

 - QWin32PrintEngine
    * [BOBUIBUG-9938] Fixed a crash on Windows 7 systems with invalid PrinterPorts
      registry entries.

 - Improved scrolling horizontally with a mouse wheel over sliders.
 - [BOBUIBUG-7451] Gestures respect panels on QGraphicsView.

BobUIOpenGL
--------

 - QOpenGLPaintEngine
    * [BOBUIBUG-10529] Fixed an issue where bound pixmaps were not released
      correctly in the GL 1 engine.

 - QGL2PaintEngineEx
    * [BOBUIBUG-8681] Fixed an application exit crash that could occur in the GL2
      engine under X11.

 - QGLContext
    * [BOBUIBUG-5732] Fixed a GLX warning that occured with some Intel chipsets
      under X11.

 - QGLPixelBuffer
    * [BOBUIBUG-8047] Fixed usage of QGLPixelBuffer with share widgets on other
      X11 screens.

 - QGLWidget
    * [BOBUIBUG-7545] Fixed QGLWidget::grabFrameBuffer() to honor the 'withAlpha' flag.
    * [BOBUIBUG-8054] Fixed drawing QPixmaps onto QGLWidgets on different X11 screens.
    * [BOBUIBUG-7865] Fixed bug where GL widgets were not fully updated on
      Windows Vista/7 with Aero disabled.
    * [BOBUIBUG-8753] Worked around driver bug causing clipping errors on the N900.
    * [BOBUIBUG-10510] Workaround ATI driver bug when using QGraphicsEffect with GL.

BobUIScript
--------

 - [BOBUIBUG-7066] Fixed regression introduced in 4.6.0 that made it impossible to
   change the prototype of the global object.
 - [BOBUIBUG-8366] Fixed regression introduced in 4.6.0 that caused the instanceof
   operator to throw an error when the right-hand-side is generated by
   QScriptEngine::newQMetaObject().
 - [BOBUIBUG-8400] Fixed memory leak when lazily binding QScriptValue to an engine.
 - [BOBUIBUG-9775] Fixed regression introduced in 4.6.0 that caused the qsTr()
   function not to resolve the translation context correctly when invoked in
   the global scope.
 - [BOBUIBUG-8364] Fixed regression introduced in QScriptclass in 4.6.0 that could
   cause the Callable extension to crash.
 - [BOBUIBUG-6437] Fixed regression introduced in QScriptEngine in 4.6.0 that made
   installTranslatorFunctions() not work with custom global object.

BobUIXml
-----

 - [BOBUIBUG-8398] QDom: prevent infinite loop when cloning a DTD.

BobUIXmlPatterns
-------------
  - [BOBUIBUG-8920] fixed crash with anonymous types in XsdSchemaChecker.
  - [BOBUIBUG-8394] include/import/redefine schemas only once.
